author: National Geographic
description: The beauty of Southern Africa's Kalahari Desert has inspired people across generations. Today, earthen-toned Desert diamonds celebrate the colors of the Kalahari, from which many originate. Through the Okavango Eternal partnership between @debeers and National Geographic, these diamonds are also helping to protect a major lifeline within this desert—the Okavango Delta and its source waters.
title: Paid content for @debeers
